:#c0392b22;color:#c0392b;border:1px solid #c0392b44;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:2px;font-size:8px;white-space:nowrap;display:inline-block">军工</span><span style="background:#27ae6022;color:#27ae60;border:1px solid #27ae6044;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:2px;font-size:8px;white-space:nowrap;display:inline-block">新能源</span></span></a><a href="https://www.cls.cn/detail/2332417" target="_blank" class="nc"><span class="nt">19:55</span><span class="nn">交易员称美股本轮劲扬主要由空头回补所致 并非伊朗和平前景</span><span class="ng"><span style="background:#7f8c8d22;color:#7f8c8d;border:1px solid #7f8c8d44;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:2px;font-size:8px;white-space:nowrap;display:inline-block">宏观</span></span></a><a href="https://www.cls.cn/detail/2332413" target="_blank" class="nc"><span class="nt">19:51</span><span class="nn">美股黄金股盘前续涨</span><span class="ng"><span style="background:#ffd70022;color:#ffd700;border:1px solid #ffd70044;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:2px;font-size:8px;white-space:nowrap;display:inline-block">贵金属</span></span></a><a href="https://www.cls.cn/detail/2332403" target="_blank" class="nc"><span class="nt">19:49</span><span class="nn">小鹏副总裁魏斌已于近期离职</span><span class="ng"><span style="background:#7f8c8d22;color:#7f8c8d;border:1px solid #7f8c8d44;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:2px;font-size:8px;white-space:nowrap;display:inline-block">宏观</span></span></a><a href="https://www.cls.cn/detail/2332402" target="_blank" class="nc"><span class="nt">19:48</span><span class="nn">胜蓝股份：控股股东及部分董事拟合计减持不超3.19%公司股份</span><span class="ng"><span style="background:#7f8c8d22;color:#7f8c8d;border:1px solid #7f8c8d44;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:2px;font-size:8px;white-space:nowrap;display:inline-block">宏观</span></span></a><a href="https://www.cls.cn/detail/2332400" target="_blank" class="nc"><span class="nt">19:46</span><span class="nn">财联社4月1日电，中国地震台网正式测定：04月01日19时20分在秘鲁（南纬7.</span><span class="ng"><span style="background:#7f8c8d22;color:#7f8c8d;border:1px solid #7f8c8d44;padding:1px 5px;border-radiu